l impact on rate performance, and\nthere exists an optimal positions of RS and IRS.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 22 Sep 2021 11:23:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 26 Mar 2022 14:21:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-29"}
