f the ROB on demand, based on a speculatively accessed secret. This reveals\nthe speculatively accessed secret, as the occupancy of the ROB itself becomes a\nnew speculative side-channel.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 22 Sep 2021 14:58:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 2 Dec 2022 08:21:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-05"}
